{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/atexit(func:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"func","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"atexit","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GVoidFunc","text":"GVoidFunc"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}],"platforms":[],"title":"atexit(func:)","externalID":"s:4GLib6atexit4funcyyyXCSg_tF","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"roleHeading":"Function"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Specifies a function to be called at normal program termination."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"atexit","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GVoidFunc","text":"GVoidFunc"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Since GLib 2.8.2, on Windows "},{"code":"g_atexit()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" actually is a preprocessor","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"macro that maps to a call to the "},{"code":"atexit()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" function in the C"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"library. This means that in case the code that calls ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_atexit()"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"i.e. "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"atexit()"},{"text":", is in a DLL, the function will be called when the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"DLL is detached from the program. This typically makes more sense"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"than that the function is called when the GLib DLL is detached,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"which happened earlier when ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_atexit()"},{"type":"text","text":" was a function in the GLib"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"DLL.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The behaviour of ","type":"text"},{"code":"atexit()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" in the context of dynamically loaded","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"modules is not formally specified and varies wildly."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On POSIX systems, calling "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_atexit()"},{"type":"text","text":" (or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"atexit()"},{"type":"text","text":") in a dynamically"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"loaded module which is unloaded before the program terminates might"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"well cause a crash at program exit."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Some POSIX systems implement ","type":"text"},{"code":"atexit()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" like Windows, and have each","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dynamically loaded module maintain an own atexit chain that is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"called when the module is unloaded."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On other POSIX systems, before a dynamically loaded module is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"unloaded, the registered atexit functions (if any) residing in that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"module are called, regardless where the code that registered them","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"resided. This is presumably the most robust approach.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"As can be seen from the above, for portability it’s best to avoid","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calling "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_atexit()"},{"text":" (or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"atexit()"},{"text":") except in the main executable of a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"program."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"atexit is deprecated:","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is best to avoid g_atexit().","type":"text"}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib"]]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/atexit(func:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"url":"\/documentation\/glib","kind":"symbol","title":"GLib","abstract":[],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","role":"collection"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/atexit(func:)":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"atexit"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"func","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GVoidFunc","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GVoidFunc"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/atexit(func:)","title":"atexit(func:)","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Specifies a function to be called at normal program termination."}],"deprecated":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/atexit(func:)","type":"topic"}}}